{"tid":632897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【洗腦防不勝防】以後睇新聞，真係要時刻警惕……","createTime":"2018-04-17T23:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T01:25:49.000Z","uid":29314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb5c715d04bc9e687217dec5576f7cff9a2ad5f","tid":632897,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T23:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/071700_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F071700_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=71ac053b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國政權要洗腦，統一口徑，要求佢控制、佢影響之下既傳媒用「標準」用詞造句去寫新聞。<br />\n<br />\n明槍易擋，暗箭難防。文匯、大公、東方、明報、TVB&hellip;&hellip;呢d公認親中既，你就話自動啟動過濾mode。你唔知本地剩餘極少數，睇黎仲係中立既傳媒老細，幾時抵受唔住誘惑、或者壓力走去跟隨。更加唔知，果堆新晉傳媒，幕後金主係邊個。<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係受老細指示，你又唔知篇文係咪由已經自小開始就洗晒腦既中國留學生、新移民執筆。（英文報導仲可以憑採訪記者既拼音，粗略分辨係中國人定香港人。）人所共知，香港地做記者，錢途麻麻、工時又長、行業唔算吸引。有人肯做已經好好，公司都唔要求得咁多。<br />\n<br />\n作為讀者，唯一可以做既，就係要時刻警惕，保持critical thinking，提防中國政府無孔不入既洗腦工程。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話，睇新聞je，使唔使做到好似防寶藥黨、電話騙案咁呀。無計啦，鬼叫「中國收回香港」咩！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">西米Go fb / ig / tumblr / twitter同步連載：</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74PgzgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=58a1e643\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74PgzgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8dbaef5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://westricego.tumblr.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwestricego.tumblr.com&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74PgzgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=6825e481\" target=\"_b